This paper discusses a replication protocol for storage systems, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the implementation of the protocol in Redis and RAMCloud storage systems, which falls under the category of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Operating Systems (cs.OS), respectively. The paper also discusses the performance improvements achieved by the protocol, which falls under the category of Databases (cs.DB) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
